ðŸ“Œ Problem Statement

In the competitive telecommunications industry, customer retention is critical for sustainable growth. The company faces a 27% churn rate, leading to significant revenue loss and higher acquisition costs.

Key challenges:

Identifying at-risk customers before they churn

Understanding root causes driving churn

Lack of visibility into vulnerable customer segments

Ineffective prioritization of retention initiatives

No predictive capability for proactive intervention

This project leverages Power BI and Random Forest machine learning to identify high-risk customers, analyze churn patterns, and enable data-driven retention strategies.
